# The Solution: {{product_name}} {{version}}

## AI That **Actually** Understands Your Business

### 🤖 Smart Automatic Generation
**{{product_name}}** analyzes your code, meetings, emails, and processes to automatically create complete documentation.

### 📝 Real-Time Updates
When you change code or a process, the documentation updates **instantly** with no manual intervention.

### 🔍 Conversational Search
Ask "_How do I set up the development environment?_" and get answers specific to your context.

### 👥 Smart Collaboration
The system suggests who should review each document and when it needs updating.

### 🎯 Role-Based Personalization
Each person sees the information relevant to their role: developer, manager, support, sales.

